Package: transltr
Title: A framework to support many languages in any R application
Version: 0.0.1.9004
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jean-Mathieu", "Potvin", , "jeanmathieupotvin@ununoctium.dev", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jérôme", "Lavoué", , "jerome.lavoue@umontreal.ca", role = c("ctb", "fnd", "rev"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4950-5475"))
  )
Description: An alternative to gettext() and xgettext() that enables
    support of many languages in any R application. Find, and extract
    source text that requires translation. Store, structure, and
    manipulate source texts and translations via R6 classes exposing a
    user-friendly API.  Easily export and import to/from a plain text
    format that fosters collaboration with other non-technical and
    external collaborators.
